text: Homonoea praecisa is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Newman in 1842. It is known from the Philippines and Borneo.BioLib.cz - Homonoea praecisa. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Homonoeini Category:Beetles described in 1842
title: Homonoea praecisa
